    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/56395629/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u56395629-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/56395629/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">鎮長</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-09-11"
      class="main-meta">2012-09-11 00:08:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5580000_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  這一系列書是寧夏人民出版推出，從英國那邊翻譯過來的， 依照它們定義的時代劃分為古代、中世紀、近代早期、拿破崙戰爭跟東方戰爭，最近又推出了帝國時代跟海上戰爭。  筆者當時買的時候是一口氣把現有的系列都收了，擺了很久，結果最近楓樹林狂出《戰略‧戰術‧兵器事典》...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5580000/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5580000_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5580000_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
